sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client<br/>(KServe Router)
    participant Gateway as Platform Ingress<br/>(KServe Gateway / Istio)<br/>TLS Termination
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DP as DataPlane<br/>Request Router
    participant Batch as Adaptive Batcher
    participant MR as ModelRegistry
    participant Model as MLModel Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/etc.)
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>PVC @ /mnt/models
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant Kafka as Kafka Cluster<br/>9092/TCP
    participant OTel as OTel Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,Gateway: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.3)
    Gateway->>REST: HTTP/8080 (plaintext)<br/>TLS terminated at gateway
    REST->>DP: Route to model handler
    DP->>Batch: Enqueue request
    Batch->>MR: Lookup model instance
    MR->>Model: predict(request)
    Model->>Storage: Load model artifacts<br/>(on first request)
    Storage-->>Model: Model files (.joblib/.bst/.onnx)
    Model-->>MR: InferenceResponse
    MR-->>Batch: Batched response
    Batch-->>DP: Response
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP 200 JSON
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    REST->>OTel: Export trace span<br/>gRPC/4317 (insecure)

    Note over Client,GRPC: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/443 (TLS)
    Gateway->>GRPC: gRPC/8081 (plaintext)
    GRPC->>DP: Route to model handler
    DP->>MR: Lookup model
    MR->>Model: predict(request)
    Model-->>MR: InferenceResponse
    MR-->>DP: Response
    DP-->>GRPC: ModelInferResponse
    GRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC/TLS Response

    Note over Kafka,Model: Flow 3: Kafka Async Inference
    Kafka-->>REST: Consume from mlserver-input<br/>9092/TCP Kafka protocol
    REST->>DP: Route async request
    DP->>MR: Lookup model
    MR->>Model: predict(request)
    Model-->>MR: InferenceResponse
    MR-->>DP: Response
    DP->>Kafka: Produce to mlserver-output<br/>9092/TCP Kafka protocol

    Note over Prom,Metrics: Flow 4: Metrics Scrape
    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8082
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(infer counts, latency, batch queue)
